<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.8">
<l>āṟāta ciṉattiṉmiku narakaṉura maḻitta vaṭalāḻit taṭakkaiya ṉalarmakaṭku maraṟkum,</l>
<l>kūṟākak koṭuttaruḷun tiruvuṭampa ṉimaiyōr kulamutalvaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>māṟāta malarkkamalañ ceṅkaḻunīr tatumpi matuveḷḷa moḻukavaya luḻavarmaṭai yaṭaippa</l>
<l>māṟāta peruñcelvam vaḷarumaṇi nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in lovely Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where unending great bounty grows,</l>
<l>Since field workers block channels so that a flood of nectar flows</l>
<l rend="indent">from unending flowering lotuses [and] red waterlilies</l>
<l rend="indent">sloshing [in the waves],</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the first in the clan of celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">happily with affection [and] rejoicing, the one with a divine body</l>
<l rend="indent">that he graciously gave in part to the lotus lady and to Hara,</l>
<l>The one in whose broad hand is the war discus which destroyed</l>
<l rend="indent">the strength of Naraka whose great rage was unmollified.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
